description:
It feels like every week this year an absolute banger of a game dropped. And while some, like Expedition 33, Split Fiction, Hades, and Silksong have definitely found huge audiences, other truly excellent games have fallen through the cracks, so here I am to tell you all about ‘em. 

From Keeper to The Séance of Blake Manor, despelote to The Roottrees Are Dead, here are some of the best games you missed in 2025.
